# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Virtual_Server — .gitignore
# Purpose: make it HARD to accidentally commit a secret from this homelab.
# WireGuard private keys, SSH private keys, and filled-in variable files must
# never land in a public repo. Only *.example / *.sample templates are tracked.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- WireGuard secrets -----------------------------------------------------
# Real tunnel configs and keys. Commit configs/wireguard/wg0.conf.example only.
wg0.conf
*.conf
!*.conf.example
privatekey
publickey
*.key
*_private.key
preshared*.key

# --- SSH private keys ------------------------------------------------------
id_rsa
id_ed25519
*.pem
*.ppk
known_hosts

# --- Infrastructure-as-Code state & real variables -------------------------
# Terraform state can contain secrets in plaintext. Never commit it.
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl
crash.log

# Ansible real inventories / vault / group_vars (commit *.example only)
inventory.ini
!inventory.example.ini
vault.yml
*.vault
group_vars/*.yml
!group_vars/*.example.yml

# --- Generic secrets / env -------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
secrets/
*.secret

# --- OS / editor noise -----------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
